            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>capers</strong> roughly&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Chop the<strong> parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>beef stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Wash the<strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"text-highlight\">baby</span> spinach </strong>and chop it roughly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
